{"tid":2331342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港政府連香港自己都可以污名化，就係唔俾人「污名化」武漢","createTime":"2020-12-18T16:53:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T16:55:41.000Z","uid":50386,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cc7f50de3038f0676ac160ad0f8ec983673fe981","tid":2331342,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T16:53:50.000Z","msg":"足癬（俗稱<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">香港腳</span></span>）通常感染腳趾間的皮膚，可能出現水泡，或皮膚乾裂脫落的病徵，患處會十分痕癢。如處理不當，患處會演變成細菌性皮膚炎，有發膿的現象。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.drugoffice.gov.hk/eps/do/tc/consumer/news_informations/knowledge_on_medicines/antitinea_drugs.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.drugoffice.gov.hk%2Feps%2Fdo%2Ftc%2Fconsumer%2Fnews_informations%2Fknowledge_on_medicines%2Fantitinea_drugs.html&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBRZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=29f02f46\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.drugoffice.gov.hk/eps/do/tc/consumer/news_informations/knowledge_on_medicines/antitinea_drugs.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u6T53Te.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu6T53Te.png&h=b34252af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港腳唔係世衛嘅正式名稱，港共一樣寫埋落去<br />\n總之自己都可以污名化<br />\n就係要奶共護主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69e2b4c118d1e3dbad5f3b2c131111b22ebd7e15","tid":2331342,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T16:55:41.000Z","msg":"唔叫得武肺，咁叫習肺囉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.ipkmedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E4%B9%8B%E7%8E%8B-King-of-viruses%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%9C%A8%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E7%9A%84%E7%8D%A8%E8%A3%81%E7%B5%B1%E6%B2%BB%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%8C%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%AD%A3%E5%9C%A8%E6%88%90%E7%88%B2%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%E7%81%BD%E9%9B%A3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipkmedia.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%